configureGemEnemy = function(enemy) 
    for i = 1, enums.TowerType.values.length do
        enemy:setTowerDamageMultiplier(enums.TowerType.values[i], 0)
    end

    for i = 1, enums.AbilityType.values.length do
        enemy:setAbilityVulnerability(enums.AbilityType.values[i], false)
    end

    enemy:setTowerDamageMultiplier(enums.TowerType.GAUSS, 1)
    enemy:setSpecialDamageVulnerability(enums.SpecialDamageType.NANOPARTICLES, false)
end

replaceDummyTile = function(placeId)
    local tiles = SP.map:getMap().tilesArray
    for i = 1, tiles.size do
        local tile = tiles.items[i]
        if tile.type == enums.TileType.DUMMY then
            local tileSpotId = tile:getData("iSpotID")
            if tileSpotId == placeId then
                local tileJson = tile:getData("STileJson")
                local newTile = managers.TileManager:createTileFromJsonString(tileJson)
                SP.map:setTile(tile:getX(), tile:getY(), newTile)
                return nil
            end
        end
    end
    log("Spot " .. tostring(placeId) .. " not found")
end
